HEADWORD: Daniel
<hw>Dan"i*el</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A Hebrew prophet
distinguished for sagacity and ripeness of judgment in youth; hence, a
sagacious and upright judge.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>Daniel</qex> come to judgment.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

